Package com.ptc.windchill.option.model

Model for the objects (Option, Choice, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.Group, and OptionSet), their masters (OptionMaster, ChoiceMaster, and OptionSetMaster), the ChoiceRules (com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceConstraint, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceEnable and com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceMapping), their masters (com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceConstraintMaster, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceEnableMaster and com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceMappingMaster), and the various links (com.ptc.windchill.option.model.OptionSetMemberLink, OptionSetChoiceRuleLink, OptionSetIgnoreChoiceRuleLink, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.RegisteredOptionSetLink, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.OverrideRegisteredOptionSetLink).

Package com.ptc.windchill.option.model Description

Model for the objects (Option, Choice, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.Group, and OptionSet), their masters (OptionMaster, ChoiceMaster, and OptionSetMaster), the ChoiceRules (com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceConstraint, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceEnable and com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceMapping), their masters (com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceConstraintMaster, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceEnableMaster and com.ptc.windchill.option.model.ChoiceMappingMaster), and the various links (com.ptc.windchill.option.model.OptionSetMemberLink, OptionSetChoiceRuleLink, OptionSetIgnoreChoiceRuleLink, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.RegisteredOptionSetLink, com.ptc.windchill.option.model.OverrideRegisteredOptionSetLink).
